high_descs: walk forwards to the kitchen counter space ahead, then take a right and walk over to the kitchen counter just a little bit to the right of the stove up ahead at the end of the room
grab a cup off of the kitchen counter space to the right of the stove
turn right and walk over to the fridge a bit ahead on the left
place the cup inside of the fridge there to cool, then take it back out once it has cooled
turn around and walked forwards just a bit, enough to end up at the kitchen sink when you then take a right and walk over to the kitchen sink
place the cup down inside of the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: place a cooled cup down inside of the kitchen sink

high_descs: Go straight ahead to the dishwasher, then turn right and go forward toward the stove.
Pick up the cup on the counter next to the stove.
Turn right and go forward, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the cup inside and chill it, then take it out.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to go to the sink.
Put the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward to the dishwasher, turn right, walk to the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the goblet next to the stove.
Turn right, walk to the refrigerator, turn left so you are facing the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the goblet on the front right of the top shelf, close the refrigerator door.  Open the refrigerator door, pick up the goblet, close the refrigerator door.
Turn completely around, walk slightly forward, turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the goblet in the sink in front of the plate.
anns.task_desc: Chill the goblet and put it in the sink.
